{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t26-example","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"一元一次方程","title":"考法2例题：裂项相消法解方程","difficulty":4,"tags":["方程","技巧","裂项"],"methodName":"裂项相消","images":["621766031479_.pic.jpg"],"pageNumber":59,"content":"解方程：$\\frac{x}{1 \\times 2} + \\frac{x}{2 \\times 3} + \\frac{x}{3 \\times 4} + \\frac{x}{4 \\times 5} + \\cdots + \\frac{x}{22 \\times 23} = 22$","steps":[{"title":"第1步：提取公因式","content":"提取方程左边的公因式 $x$。","formula":"x \\left( \\frac{1}{1 \\times 2} + \\frac{1}{2 \\times 3} + \\cdots + \\frac{1}{22 \\times 23} \\right) = 22"},{"title":"第2步：裂项相消","content":"利用公式 $\\frac{1}{n(n+1)} = \\frac{1}{n} - \\frac{1}{n+1}$：\n$\\left(1 - \\frac{1}{2}\\right) + \\left(\\frac{1}{2} - \\frac{1}{3}\\right) + \\cdots + \\left(\\frac{1}{22} - \\frac{1}{23}\\right) = 1 - \\frac{1}{23} = \\frac{22}{23}$","formula":""},{"title":"第3步：求解方程","content":"$x \\times \\frac{22}{23} = 22 \\Rightarrow x = 22 \\times \\frac{23}{22} = 23$","formula":"x = 23"}]},"id":"t26"},"__N_SSG":true}